title: Ennum Eppozhum
subTitle: Vineeth, a magazine reporter, lacks the inspiration to work hard. However, his life takes a turn when he is asked to interview a family court lawyer.

title: Monayi Angane Aanayi
subTitle: Monayi goes to the city to stay with his friend. However, he ends up getting involved in problems which turns chaotic for everyone.

title: Jananam 1947 Pranayam Thudarunnu
subTitle: In a care home for the elderly, two senior citizens forge a heartwarming connection, embarking on a shared path of love and companionship.

title: Hailesa
subTitle: Unnikrishnan is forced to move to the city after he beats up some thugs for his foster family. In the city, he starts working for Ganapathy Iyer, a rich man who is seeking his long-lost lover.

title: June
subTitle: June, a teenager, believes that there is nothing remarkable about her. She experiences adolescent crushes, handles heartbreaks and fights insecurities as she grows into a mature and confident woman.

title: One
subTitle: An aspiring policeman embarks on an unauthorised mission to investigate a devious scientist. However, he confronts various challenges when his actions are exposed.

title: Snehaveedu
subTitle: Ajayan comes back to his village to be with his ailing mother. However, things get strange when a boy comes to his house claiming to be his son.

title: Oru Vadakkan Selfie
subTitle: When his father asks him to manage their grocery store, Umesh runs away to Chennai to become a film-maker. His life changes after he takes a selfie with his old neighbour and posts it online.

title: Lucifer
subTitle: The demise of the leader of a political party leads to a massive power struggle. Amidst the chaos, a mystical man named Stephen comes in to ascend the throne.

title: Love Action Drama
subTitle: Dinesh, a conceited and wealthy young bachelor, goes to extreme lengths to impress a girl named Shobha with the help of his best friend Sagar, and Dinesh eventually hopes to marry Shobha.

title: Love Action Drama

title: Iyobinte Pusthakam
subTitle: Returning to his village after the war to meet his family, Aloshy discovers that his brothers are working as henchmen for a local businessman and plotting against his father.

title: Kili Poyi
subTitle: Friends Chacko and Hari are fed up with their employer and plan a trip to Goa. Their trip turns into something unusual when they discover a mysterious bag.

title: Karutha Pakshikal
subTitle: Widower Murugan moves to Kerala with his three children and irons clothes to make a living. While dealing with daily issues, he also aims to fund the operation of his child who is visually impaired.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Masters
subTitle: Milan Paul and Sreeramakrishnan are very good friends and always help each other out. They soon try to unravel the mystery behind a series of murders and suicides that hits the town.

title: Natturajavu
subTitle: Pulikkattil, an affluent family man, is forced to bear the brunt and burden of his late father's unscrupulous past. Now, Karnan, a jail convict, decides to settle some old scores with him.

title: Kantara
subTitle: When greed paves the way for betrayal, scheming and murder, a young tribal reluctantly dons the traditions of his ancestors to seek justice.

title: Manjummel Boys
subTitle: After one of them falls inside a dangerous pit in the Guna Caves, a group of childhood friends muster courage to rescue him out of a space from where a return is next to impossible.

title: Oru Yamandan Premakadha
subTitle: Lallu, a happy-go-lucky person who loves to hang out with his friends, is in pursuit of true love. One day, he finds a photo of a missing woman, Diya, in the newspaper and feels a spark.

title: Action Hero Biju
subTitle: Biju Poulose leaves his teaching job to pursue his dream of serving in the police force. Posted as the sub-inspector in Cochin, he has to handle notorious criminals who indulge in unlawful activities.

title: Action Hero Biju
subTitle: Biju Poulose leaves his teaching job to pursue his dream of serving in the police force. Posted as the sub-inspector in Cochin, he has to handle notorious criminals who indulge in unlawful activities.

title: Greetings
subTitle: Gopan falls in love with his neighbour, Sheethal. After learning that Sheetal has a plan to reunite a separated couple, he also pools in ideas, which leads to many unexpected events.

title: Sullu
subTitle: Jithu, a carefree boy, gets trapped in an abandoned house, forcing him to reflect on his life and appreciate what he once took for granted.

title: Oru Black and White Kudumbam
subTitle: Antony, a lorry driver, struggles with an inferiority complex stemming from his skin colour, leading him to create ongoing problems for his family.

title: Vakkalathu Narayanankutty
subTitle: Narayankutty wishes to be a lawyer but ends up being a clerk in a government office. However, when he sees the law being breached or misused, he does not hesitate to raise his voice against it.

title: Kammatti Paadam
subTitle: Krishnan returns home to Kammattippaadam after a call from his friend Ganga. Together, they face their dark past as old crimes resurface, putting their lives in danger.

title: Ittymaani: Made in China
subTitle: Ittymaani, who was raised in China, runs a business of counterfeit products in India. However, when he tries to help Annamma who is ignored by her sons, he lands in trouble because she falls ill.

title: Thanneermathan Dinangal
subTitle: Jaison, a teenager, has a crush on Keerthy, but she does not reciprocate his feelings. To make things worse, he gets in trouble with Ravi, the new teacher who is liked by everyone, especially Keerthy.

title: Pulimurugan
subTitle: A small village seeks help from a man with extraordinary force to protect them against man-eating tigers and the drug mafia.

title: Irupathiyonnam noottandu
subTitle: Appu, a restaurateur and surfer based in Goa, falls in love with Zaya. When she goes back home to Kerala, Appu takes it upon himself to find her and confess his feelings.
